    {
      "id": "https://radiantjxn.churchcenter.com/registrations/events/3558367",
      "title": "Costa Rica | Sign Up Deadline",
      "url": "https://radiantjxn.churchcenter.com/registrations/events/3558367",
      "startsAt": "2026-04-12T04:00:00.000Z",
      "endsAt": "2026-04-12T22:00:00.000Z",
      "dateLabel": "Apr 12, 2026",
      "imageUrl": "https://registrations-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/event/logo/3558367/medium_image-1774880868809.jpeg",
      "summary": "<div><p><strong>Costa Rica Missions Trip</strong></p><p>Join us as we partner with Pastor Armando and his church in Costa Rica to help support their growing ministry and new church location. During this trip, our team will assist with construction on the new building, distribute food within the community, and host worship, teaching, and evangelistic outreach in the evenings. It will be a meaningful opportunity to serve, share the love of Christ, and support what God is doing through the local church.</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>A valid passport that does not expire within six months of your return date.</li></ul><p><strong>Cost</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Total Trip Cost:</strong> $2,000<br>(Includes trip expenses, ministry projects, and estimated travel costs.)</li></ul><p><strong>Payment Schedule</strong></p><ul><li><strong>$500 deposit due at registration</strong> – April 12</li><li><strong>Remaining $1,500 due by</strong> Sep. 17</li></ul><p><strong>Who Can Join</strong></p><ul><li>Must be <strong>18 or older</strong> to register alone.</li><li><strong>Minors</strong> must be accompanied by a parent or guardian. Please send an email to jallen@radiantjxn.com to register a minor.&nbsp;</li></ul><div></div></div>",
      "showEventTime": true
    },
    {
      "id": "https://radiantjxn.churchcenter.com/registrations/events/3180657",
      "title": "Next Steps Class | Sycamore",
      "url": "https://radiantjxn.churchcenter.com/registrations/events/3180657",
      "startsAt": "2026-04-12T04:00:00.000Z",
      "endsAt": "2026-04-19T04:00:00.000Z",
      "dateLabel": "April 12–19, 2026",
      "imageUrl": "https://registrations-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/event/logo/3180657/medium_image-1758904485718.jpg",
      "summary": "<div><p>Next Steps is a gathering designed to accelerate us into full engagement with Jesus and His purpose for our life. If you're new to Radiant, your spiritual growth has plateaued or you just need a little help finding what your next step is, this group is for you.&nbsp;</p><p><em>It is important you are able to attend both sessions, if you have a conflict please select another session.</em><br><br>Radiant Kids is available during each of our Sunday services.</p><div></div></div>",
      "showEventTime": true
    },
    {
      "id": "https://radiantjxn.churchcenter.com/registrations/events/3544134",
      "title": "RISE UP | A Women's Event",
      "url": "https://radiantjxn.churchcenter.com/registrations/events/3544134",
      "startsAt": "2026-04-24T04:00:00.000Z",
      "endsAt": "2026-04-25T00:30:00.000Z",
      "dateLabel": "Apr 24, 2026",
      "imageUrl": "https://registrations-production.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/event/logo/3544134/medium_image-1774289279070.jpeg",
      "summary": "<div><p>Join us on April 24th at 6:30 PM for our very first women’s event—<strong>RISE UP!</strong></p><p>This special evening is all about stepping boldly into your God-given calling as a woman of faith. Through powerful worship, encouraging messages, and meaningful fellowship,&nbsp; you’ll gather together to be strengthened, uplifted, and inspired to RISE UP. Enjoy this evening with charcuterie and a make-your-own bouquet bar—designed for you to relax, connect, and be refreshed.<br><br>We hope to see you there!</p><p>Please note: Radiant Kids will not be available for this event.</p><div></div></div>",
      "showEventTime": true
    },
    {
