      "summary": "<div><p>If you are a new believer or have never been baptized, we encourage you to sign up today and take the next step in your walk with God and be a part of Water Baptisms on May 3rd at both of our campuses. Water Baptism is one of the ways we identify ourselves with Christ. It’s an outward expression of what God has done in us.</p><p><strong>The deadline to sign up for baptisms is April 28th.</strong></p><div></div></div>",
